metadata.description: The Shiba Platinum Official is an Platinum club for the baddest of the Shiba Platinum Token. Our 2D NFT collection has 5.000 unique hand-drawn Shiba Platinum with the best detail in the industry. All Shiba Platinum NFT holders will automatically receive 10,000 #SHIBA Platinum Tokens on their wallet.
